    • Method Detail

      • createLog

        public void createLog()
        Creates an auditable log file, loops through the elected HashMap and writes the name of the elected candidate and all associated ballots in the order they were elected. At the end, writes the election type, the number of seats, and number of candidates to the log file as well.

      • fileErrors

        public void fileErrors()
        Handles any file related errors if they occur. Writes an error message to the log file to inform the user that an error occured during the election
